[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":78},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fcategories\u002Fjavascript\u002Fpage\u002F21\u002F":3,"category-page:zh-Hant:javascript:21":4,"author-stats:zh-Hant:full":75},null,{"category":5,"posts":6,"total":73,"totalPages":74},"JavaScript",[7,14,22,28,35,41,48,56,62,68],{"url":8,"title":9,"date":10,"updated":3,"category":5,"tags":11,"description":12,"readingMinutes":13},"\u002Fjavascript\u002F20190624\u002F604717444\u002F","嘗試了解 JavaScript 的原型鏈","2019-06-24 12:28:48",[5],"這一篇其實我一直猶豫該不該寫，因為我深怕一個地方紀錄錯了會導致其他看的人也跟著錯，但是想一想我當初撰寫 Hexo 部落格的初衷是做自己的筆記後就又好點了，這一篇來記錄一下 JavaScript 的原型鏈這個主題","3",{"url":15,"title":16,"date":17,"updated":3,"category":5,"tags":18,"description":20,"readingMinutes":21},"\u002Fjavascript\u002F20190621\u002F538821393\u002F","CoffeeScript 三元運算子","2019-06-21 11:49:07",[5,19],"CoffeeScript","這邊紀錄一下 CoffeeScript 的三元運算子該如何撰寫","1",{"url":23,"title":24,"date":25,"updated":3,"category":5,"tags":26,"description":27,"readingMinutes":21},"\u002Fjavascript\u002F20190621\u002F4177225789\u002F","CoffeeScript event 沒有反應","2019-06-21 10:19:54",[5,19],"撰寫 CoffeeScript 的時候發生一件怪事情，event 事件竟然無法使用，所以這邊紀錄一下我曾經做過哪些事情以及解決方式",{"url":29,"title":30,"date":31,"updated":3,"category":5,"tags":32,"description":33,"readingMinutes":34},"\u002Fjavascript\u002F20190620\u002F3794703376\u002F","CoffeeScript 基礎學習","2019-06-20 10:52:16",[5,19],"由於可能專案使用上的需求將會撰寫 CoffeeScript，所以這邊就來稍微摸一下 CoffeeScript 是什麼鬼，又可以用什麼方式來撰寫","2",{"url":36,"title":37,"date":38,"updated":3,"category":5,"tags":39,"description":40,"readingMinutes":34},"\u002Fjavascript\u002F20190619\u002F3418592009\u002F","JavaScript 扁平化多維陣列","2019-06-19 14:45:37",[5],"今天遇到一個需求需要將多維陣列扁平化，這邊紀錄一下我查到的資料該怎麼做，順便記錄一下今天看到的 ES 2019 的方式",{"url":42,"title":43,"date":44,"updated":3,"category":5,"tags":45,"description":47,"readingMinutes":34},"\u002Fjavascript\u002F20190618\u002F3285272502\u002F","GitHub API contents file date 亂碼解決方法","2019-06-18 11:40:06",[5,46],"GitHub","這幾天在使用 GitHub API 中的一個 API 方法發現 content 會出現亂碼問題，這邊紀錄一下該如何解決 content 亂碼",{"url":49,"title":50,"date":51,"updated":3,"category":5,"tags":52,"description":55,"readingMinutes":34},"\u002Fjavascript\u002F20190617\u002F3829122039\u002F","使用 Google Apps Script 解決 CORS 問題","2019-06-17 13:24:47",[5,53,54],"Google Apps Script","CORS","前端打 API 遇到 CORS 又沒法改後端怎麼辦？這一篇從同源政策（Same-origin policy）的概念講起，用 Google Apps Script 包一層 Proxy 把第三方 API 變成你自己的同源 API， 繞過 CORS 限制。",{"url":57,"title":58,"date":59,"updated":3,"category":5,"tags":60,"description":61,"readingMinutes":34},"\u002Fjavascript\u002F20190614\u002F4085828838\u002F","ES6 Template String 雙陣列處理方式","2019-06-14 20:11:14",[5],"今天在撰寫 JavaScript 的時候發生一件事情，就是在 ES6 中的 Template String 在處理一次陣列的方式，這邊做一下紀錄怎麼處理",{"url":63,"title":64,"date":65,"updated":3,"category":5,"tags":66,"description":67,"readingMinutes":34},"\u002Fjavascript\u002F20190530\u002F3821927811\u002F","JavaScript 非同步與同步事件之 async","2019-05-30 12:03:13",[5],"上一章節已經講完 await 後接下來當然是 async 啦，有同步就有非同步，所以這邊來記錄一下 async。",{"url":69,"title":70,"date":65,"updated":3,"category":5,"tags":71,"description":72,"readingMinutes":34},"\u002Fjavascript\u002F20190530\u002F2986904348\u002F","JavaScript 非同步與同步事件之 await",[5],"前面已經講解完 Promise 所以接下來就是講 async 與 await 是什麼東西，但是我會將這兩個東西拆開來講解做紀錄，首先先講講 await。",220,22,{"postCount":76,"tagCount":77},1035,1009,1784013046021]